Dia biasa melecehkan perempuan!

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:14.280
Dan itulah sebabnya saya memecatnya!

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:19.080
Dia menikahi saudara perempuan Shakti!

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:21.000
Sempurna.

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:25.160
Oke.  Kirimkan semua detailnya kepada saya.

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:27.160
Sekarang.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:33.760
Shakti Sharma.

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:37.040
Terakhir kali, Anda memenangkan pertarungan.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:41.160
Kali ini, saya akan menang.

00:10:41.560 --> 00:10:43.040
Dan bersamamu,

00:10:43.800 --> 00:10:46.360
seluruh keluargamu akan kalah.

